# [Siege Spider](https://siegespider.cc)

<a href="https://gitHub.com/Haste171/siege-spider-dashboard/graphs/commit-activity"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Maintained%3F-no-red.svg">
<a href="https://github.com/Haste171/siege-spider-dashboard/blob/master/LICENSE"><img src="https://img.shields.io/github/license/Haste171/langchain-chatbot">

Siege spider is a free [Rainbow Six Siege](https://www.google.com/search?q=Tom+Clancy%27s+Rainbow+Six+Siege%0D%0A&sca_esv=58ed7cc7eaa43e58&ei=j_7faJ7oFqqk0PEP2fT5YA&ved=0ahUKEwje65yQvoiQAxUqEjQIHVl6HgwQ4dUDCBA&uact=5&oq=Tom+Clancy%27s+Rainbow+Six+Siege%0D%0A&gs_-AEB-AECmAIDoAIeqAIUwgIKEAAYsAMY1gQYR8ICDRAAGIAEGLADGEMYigXCAg4QABiwAxjkAhjWBNgBAcICExAuGIAEGLADGEMYyAMYigXYAQGYAwniAwUSATEgQPEFzPr5TyhoOoeIBgGQBhG6BgYIARABGAm6BgQIAhgHkgcBM6AHpxOyBwC4BwDCBwUyLTEuMsgHGQ&sclient=gws-wiz-serp) stat tracking application I created as an alternative to platforms like [R6Tracker](https://r6.tracker.network), [stats.cc](https://stats.cc/siege), [R6Analyst](https://r6analyst.com). The goal was to combine all the greatest features/attributes of all these platforms into one simplified de-bloated application with a couple nice features added on top.
